Me too. If it doesn't smell sweet and doesn't look orangish it's probably ok. If you have doubts of the efficacy of the fuel, you can always pour in some new gas of a slightly higher grade.

I burned some year old gas in my motorcycle and it smelled and looked ok. The bike didn't seem to care either.

